'''Mali''' ke naga lefasaneng la [[Afrika]]. ''Mali'' e bodikela ba [[Afrika]], e wela seleteng sa [[Afrika Bodikela]].

''Mali'' ke e tee ya dinaga tše hlano [[Afrika]], [[landlocked|tšeo di sa bapago le lewatle]].


''Mali'' e agišane le : 
* [[Algeria]] (borwa),
* [[Niger]] (bohlabela),
* [[Burkina Faso]] and the [[Côte d'Ivoire]] (borwa),
* [[Guinea]] (borwa bodikela),
* [[Senegal]] and [[Mauritania]] (bodikela).

